OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNew mum Yvette Cooper hid  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffrom boss Tony Blair as she
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Flooked after child         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Labour's Yvette Cooper has revealed    
OL,6, that she once hid from Tony Blair while
OL,7, she looked after her young child.      
OL,9,FThe shadow home secretary told the     
OL,10,FBBC's Political Thinking podcast that, 
OL,11,Fin her early days in politics, women   
OL,12,FMPs had been reluctant to be seen      
OL,13,F"juggling" work and family duties.     
OL,15,FAs a result, she had feared not looking
OL,16,F"professional" in front of the then PM,
OL,17,Fwho was boarding a train she was on.   
OL,19,FMs Cooper had three children after     
OL,20,Fentering Parliament in 1997, aged 28.  
